    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Base class for platform-dependent code handling touchpad events</para>
<para>If you want to add touchpad gesture support on your platform, inherit this class, extend the <computeroutput><ref refid="classMR_1_1TouchpadController_1a7f99ad050f7c266930af4bf9ffc13c37" kindref="member">TouchpadController::initialize</ref></computeroutput> method and call the corresponding methods on the touchpad events. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
